OL,3,CCustomers 'will get compensation' say
OL,4,CSouth West Water after supply
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,FWith more than 9,500 properties -
OL,8,Fincluding homes, schools and
OL,9,Fbusinesses - were experiencing water
OL,10,Fissues on Tuesday 22 April after the
OL,11,Fburst at the Dousland water treatment
OL,12,Fworks on Monday 21 April.
OL,14,FHomes in Tavistock, Bere Alston, and
OL,15,FYelverton have been impacted while at
OL,16,Fleast four schools have been forced to
OL,17,Fclose.
