OL,3,CCustomers 'will get compensation' say
OL,4,CSouth West Water after supply
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,FAt 7.30am on Wednesday 23 April, South
OL,8,FWest Water released a statement
OL,9,Fsaying: "We are pleased to say that
OL,10,Fcustomers should now be back in supply.
OL,12,F"We want to apologise again for the
OL,13,Finconvenience this has caused, but we
OL,14,Fwould also like to thank all of our
OL,15,Fcustomers for their patience and
OL,16,Fkindness to our teams on the ground
OL,17,Fproviding bottled water."
OL,19,FLocal MP speaks out
