OL,7,FFred Thomas, Labour MP for Plymouth
OL,8,FMoor View, said he'd spoken to South
OL,9,FWest Water's chief executive Susan
OL,10,FDavy and "demanded a fair compensation
OL,11,Fpackage" for all those impacted.
OL,13,FIn a series of messages posted on X,
OL,14,FMr Thomas said: "I demanded a fair
OL,15,Fcompensation package for residents and
OL,16,Fbusiness.
